citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
* A facility representative was not available on 11/10/15 at 1:30 PM to do a facility inspection.
* Inspector knocked on the front door of the licensees house. Inspector called telephone numbers given by the
licensee. Inspector waited required 30 minute time for licensee to show up.
* Copy of inspection report was sent by regular mail.
Additional Inspectors
Owens Amanda, Veterinary Medical Officer
